The chip consists of 2 PMMA parts; the lower part contains the engraved channel structure, and the upper part contains inlet ports, as shown in Fig. 1a. The produced channel is done by direct-write laser machining technique. VLS3.5 UNEVERSAL LASER SYSTEMS with a 30-W CO2 laser tube and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
